\mt1 Seken Pita  
\imt1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ô rani m…ô n…ôfe i n…ôkuku…ô  
\ip N…ôp…®n riti ipaka t…® nuk 66, Pita r…®rai n…ôkuku…ô s…ô ro k…ôru ir…ô rev…ôn t…® nakalasia me fwe profens n…ôha kani m…ô Esia Maenor. N…ômis…ôien s…ô k…®namo ia nakalasia me n…ôha fwe Esia Maenor r…®no sampam. M…ôt…ô nahat…ôn eiku…ô me h…ôuvehe mwi t…® nir…ôha. Pita r…®ni pen t…® nakalasia me m…ô ir…ôha tuh…ôukur…ôn amasan nari n…ôn…ô mh…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha. Noien n…ôha tr…ôkoui raka nahat…ôn eiku…ô me t…® nir…ôha. Pita r…®ni pen m…ô Kumwes…ôn trouraha nahat…ôn eiku…ô me. T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô Iesu Kristo truvehe mwi, Pita r…®ni pen t…® nakalasia me m…ô tuhar…ô ia nar…ôien s…ô ro ikinan.  
\c 1  
\p
\v 1 Iou Saemon Pita, iou i…ôrmama riti s…ô iakamo tukwini nari m Iesu Kristo, n…ôn…ô, iou aposol riti s…ôv…ônhi.  
\p Iakamrai n…ôkuku…ô i m k…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme hiam…ôuvehi nahat…ôt…ôien riti s…ô krouamasan p…®k rou…ômn…ômwhen a ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®maha. Hiam…ôuvehi nahat…ôt…ôien ia noien atukwatukw s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn m…®ne i…ôrmama s…ô rauvehim…®ru k…®taha Iesu Kristo.   
\p
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt Jut 2\x*Pw…ôh namasanien m…®ne n…ôm…ôrinuien krouvehe rouasori mwi tukumiaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô hi…ôukur…ôn Kumwes…ôn m…®ne Iesu I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha.   
\s1 Noien me n…ôrmama tuho trahat…ôn pen m…ô ir…ôha h…ôukur…ôn amasan Iesu Kristo  
\p
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt 1Tes 2:9\x*Ia n…®skaiien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn, in ruvei pehe m k…®taha narimnari me pam s…ôm…ôme tsam…ôkeikei mh…ôuvehi s…ôv…ôi n…®m…®ruien m…®ne noien me s…ôm…ôme hatukwatukw n…ôn…ô rer…®n ra…°ien tukwe. Narimnari me n…ôha h…ôm…ôier pehe tukutaha t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô k…®taha s…ôukur…ôn Kumwes…ôn s…ô in r…®n…ôkwein k…®taha m…ô ts…ôuvehi p…ôri nasoriien s…ôv…ônhi m…®ne namasanien s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 4 Ia narimnari me n…ôha, in r…®m…ôuvei pehe m k…®taha promes keikei me s…ôv…ônhi hasori p…®k. In r…®m…ôuvei pehe promes me i m…ô tih…ôuvehi pw…ôh hasitu ia k…®miaha hiaraka ia noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ôi t…®pr…ôn…ô i s…ôm…ôme kamhouraha n…ôrmama t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha hokeikei p…®k m…ô tuho, n…ôn…ô hi…ôukur…ôn nuveheien mho kuatia ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn.   
\p
\v 5 Ro iam…®nha ir…ô k…®miaha tiham…ôkeikei mhousari mhakutan pen noien me i ia nahat…ôt…ôien s…ôk…®miaha. Tih…ôkupw…ôn mhakutan pen noien amasan, n…ôn…ô, n…ôp…®n hi…ônakutan pen raka i, hiakutan pen mwi nukur…ônien,  
\v 6 \x - \xo 1:6 \xt Kal 5:22-23\x*n…ôn…ô, n…ôp…®n hi…ônakutan pen raka i, hiakutan pen mwi noien i s…ô hiam…ôkoui atukw k…®miaha, n…ôn…ô, n…ôp…®n hi…ônakutan pen raka i, hiakutan pen mwi n…ôrerien s…ô hiam…ôrer …ôknek…®n ir…ô ia n…ôp…®n me, n…ôn…ô, n…ôp…®n hi…ônakutan pen raka i, hiakutan pen mwi noien i s…ô hiamo narimnari me s…ôm…ôme Kumwes…ôn rokeikei,  
\v 7 n…ôn…ô, n…ôp…®n hi…ônakutan pen raka i, hiakutan pen mwi nokeikeiien i s…ô hiamokeikei pi…ôvtaha me ir…ô, n…ôn…ô, n…ôp…®n hi…ônakutan pen raka i, hiakutan pen mwi nokeikeiien i s…ô hiamokeikei n…ôrmama me pam ir…ô.  
\v 8 Ramasan m…ô tiho noien me n…ôha. N…ôp…®n noien me n…ôha rasori p…®k ia n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha, ro k…®miaha hi…ôpkar…ô au…ôr a mh…ô, m…ôt…ô k…®maha tih…ôukur…ôn amasan Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha, n…ôn…ô n…®m…®ruien s…ôk…®miaha truku…ô mo kw…ônkwan.  
\v 9 M…ôt…ô i…ôrmama s…ô r…®pko mh…ô noien me n…ôha in r…ômwhen i…ôrmama s…ô n…ônimen r…®fw…ô ko r…®pk…ôti pen mh…ô isipw…®n, n…ôn…ô in r…®nenouenou m…ô Iesu r…®naikuas raka noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônhi s…ôm…ôme in r…®no fwe kupw…ôn.   
\p
\v 10 Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô piak me tiham…ôkeikei mhousari …ôknek…®n m…ô tiho noien me n…ôha, n…ôn…ô ramahat…ôn pen m…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®m…ôrfi p…ôrhien k…®miaha, m…ôkwein k…®miaha m…ô k…®miaha n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi. Ro pen tr…®ni m…®nu…ô hiamo noien me n…ôha ko hi…ôpk…®mwei mh…ô n…ôp…®n riti.  
\v 11 N…ôn…ô n…ôp…®n Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha truvehe ir…ô, in truvehim…®ru k…®miaha, n…ôn…ô, m…ôseni k…®miaha hi…ôuvnimw…ô ia n…®t…ôt…ô s…ôv…ônhi s…ô in tr…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô ia nuk nuk me.   
\s1 N…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi profet me ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan  
\p
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt Jut 5\x*Ro pen n…ôp…®n me pam takam…ôkeikei mo a pw…ôh rer…®miaha ramrhi narimnari me i, n…ôri au…ôr a m…ô hi…ôukur…ôn n…ôn…ô mamh…ôrer …ôknek…®n ia n…®p…ôrhienien s…ô hi…ôuv…ôuvehi raka.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 1:13 \xt 2Tes 3:1\x*N…ôp…®n iakam…®ru ihi ia n…®pwrak i, rer…®k ramrhi m…ô ratukwatukw m…ô tak…®ni n…ô…°kiariien i m…ôsu…ôpwiri k…®miaha ir…ô pw…ôh rer…®miaha ramrhi,  
\v 14 \x - \xo 1:14 \xt 2Kor 5:1, Jon 21:18-19\x*t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô iakukur…ôn m…ô tr…®pko mh…ô tui iakemh…ô, m…ôpw…ôh n…®pwrak i r…ômwhen ia Iesu Kristo I…ôr…®m…ônu s…ôk…®taha ruv…ôni pehe raka tukw iou i.  
\v 15 N…ôn…ô takam…ôkeikei m…ômwur n…ôha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni m…ô tih…ôpw…ôh nenouenouien ia narimnari me i n…ôp…®n iakuvamh…ô raka mier ia t…®pr…ôn…ô i.   
\p
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Mat 17:1-5\x*N…ôp…®n iaham…ôni irapw tukumiaha m…ô Iesu Kristo truvehe mwi ia n…®skaiien, iah…ôpk…®ni mh…ô kw…ôna…°ei me ir…ô s…ôm…ôme i…ôrmama rani a ia n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônhi, m…ôt…ô k…®mrahar iahar…ôn…ôtoni atukwatukw ia n…ônimemrahar n…®skaiien m…®ne nukuraanien asori s…ôv…ônhi.  
\v 17-18 \x - \xo 1:17-18 \xt Mat 17:5\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô fwe kupw…ôn, k…®mrahar\f + \fr 1:17-18 \ft Ir…ôhar n…ô Pita, Jemes, m…®ne Jon\f* iahamarav…ôn ia t…ôku…ôr ikinan k…®maha Iesu. Ia n…ôp…®n n…ôha Tata Kumwes…ôn ruvei pen n…®siaien m Iesu, n…ôn…ô mo nukuraanien r…ôhiapw mier ia n…®pwran, n…ôn…ô reri Kumwes…ôn r…®ni m…ô, ‚ÄúIn i n…ôr…®k keikei, rer…®k ra…°ien p…®k tukwe.‚Äù K…®mrahar iaharre…°i n…ô…°kiariien n…ôha ruku pen fwe ia neiai muvehe.   
\p
\v 19 K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn mwi m…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi profet kupw…ôn me ro n…®p…ôrhienien. Ramasan m…ô k…®miaha tih…ôt…ôr…®…° amasan ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi profet kupw…ôn me r…ômwhen ia laet s…ô ram…ôhiapw ia n…ôpit…ôvien. Laet n…ôha tram…ôhiapw iam…®nha ir…ô meste ruv…ôran pen ia n…ôp…®n asori n…ôha n…ôn…ô kouf…ôt…ôtei…ô rut…ô ia rer…®miaha.  
\v 20 \fig Ram…ôvsini n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi Kumwes…ôn|alt="Unrollin…° a scroll" src="LB00279B.TIF" size="col" copy="Horace Knowles" ref="2Pit 1:19-20" \fig*N…ôri s…ô tih…ôkupw…ôn mh…ôukur…ôn ro iam…®nhi ir…ô. N…ô…°kiariien me pam s…ôv…ôi profet me ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan riti riw…ôn in n…ô…°kiariien atukw s…ôv…ôi profet riti.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt 2Tim 3:16, 1Pit 1:11\x*Iakani iam…®nhi ir…ô t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô profet me h…ônapk…®ni irapw mh…ô n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien atukw s…ôv…ônraha, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme N…ôn…®mw…®n Ikinan riri ir…ôha mo ir…ôha h…ôni irapw n…ô…°kiariien s…ô ruku pen t…® Kumwes…ôn.   
\c 2  
\s1 Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me Kumwes…ôn trouraha ir…ôha  
\p
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt Mat 24:11, Jut 4\x*M…ôt…ô fwe kupw…ôn profet eiku…ô me n…ôha ik…®n ia reri n…ôkur Isrel. Ia noien a mwi n…ôha k…®miaha tih…ôtoni nahat…ôn eiku…ô me ia rer…®miaha. Ir…ôha tuh…ôuvehe afafa, mhahat…ôn k…®miaha ia neiku…ôien me s…ôm…ôme tuhouraha nari. Ir…ôha tuh…ôni m…ô rek…ôm r…®pko mh…ô Iesu in i…ôm…ô asori s…ô r…®n…ôr…ôku raka ir…ôha meivinari ia nir…ôha. T…® noien n…ôha kamho Kumwes…ôn trouraha akwauakw ir…ôha.  
\v 2 N…ôrmama h…ôp…®k tuh…ôkurir…ô pen nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha ia noien …ôr…ôha s…ô ir…ôha kamho ramo naur…®sien. Ro iam…®nhi ir…ô n…ôrmama nepw…®n mwi tuh…ôni …ôr…ôha suatuk s…ôv…ôi n…®p…ôrhienien.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 2:3 \xt Rom 16:18, 1Tes 2:5\x*T…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha hokeikei p…®k mane, ir…ôha tuh…ôni neiku…ôien me m k…®miaha m…ô tih…ôuvei pen mane m…®nraha. Kumwes…ôn ruv…ôni raka tui ia N…ôkuku…ô Ikinan m…ô tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha, n…ôn…ô, m…®n…ôrer mwatuk m…ô trouraha ir…ôha m…ôpw…ôh napriien.   
\p
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Jut 6\x*K…®miaha hi…ôukur…ôn. Fwe kupw…ôn, n…ôp…®n na…°elo me nepw…®n h…ôno noien …ôr…ôha, Kumwes…ôn r…®pk…ôkwt…ômhiri mh…ô n…ôrpw…®nien s…ôv…ônraha, m…ôt…ô r…®n…ôrihi ir…ôha ia jen, m…ôrarki pen ir…ôha ia kwopun riti fwe inh…ôr…®pw\f + \fr 2:4 \ft Ia n…ô…°kiariien Krik, kwopun n…ôha inh…ôr…®pw s…ô Pita rani n…ô…°h…®n n…ô Tartaros. N…ôkur Kris h…ôm…ôni kwopun n…ôha m…ô kwopun kam…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me ik…®n s…ôv…ôi n…ôn…®mw…®n …ôr…ôha me m…®ne n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme h…ôn…ôrui n…ôkwai Kumwes…ôn.\f* m…ô tuhamar…ô ik…®n ia n…ôpit…ôvien meste n…ôp…®n in tr…ôrpw…®n noien …ôr…ôha me ir…ô.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt Jen 6-8, 8:18, 2Tes 3:6\x*N…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®pk…ôkwt…ômhiri mh…ô n…ôrpw…®nien s…ôv…ôi n…ôrmama kupw…ôn me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrui n…ôkwan ia n…ôp…®n s…ôv…ôi Noa, m…ôt…ô r…®nouraha ir…ôha ia nui asori. M…ôt…ô Noa r…®m…ôni irapw n…ô…°kiariien s…ôv…ôi noien atukwatukw, n…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn ruvehim…®ru in m…®ne n…ôrmama me s…ôv…ônhi ir…ôha pam sefen.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 2:6 \xt Jen 19:24, Jut 7\x*N…ôn…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®no n…ôrpw…®nien t…® n…ôr…ôhaien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur Sotom m…®ne Komora, r…®m…ôuvani taon mi n…ôha ia napw krouo n…®mwrakw ia nirau. In ro iam…®nha ir…ô m…ô trahat…ôn n…ôfe tro m n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôrui n…ôkwan.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 2:7 \xt Jen 19:1-16\x*M…ôt…ô in r…®m…ôuvehim…®ru Lot. I…ôm…ô n…ôha in i…ôm…ô atukwatukw, n…ôn…ô rer…®n ram…ômis…ô t…® noien …ôr…ôha s…ô ramo naur…®sien s…ôv…ôi n…ôkur …ôr…ôha me n…ôha ik…®n.  
\v 8 In ramar…ô ir…ôha m…®nraha, mam…ôtoni noien …ôr…ôha me n…ôha kamho, mamre…°i n…ô…°kiariien …ôr…ôha me n…ôha kamh…ôni, ia n…ôp…®n me pam rer…®n s…ô ratukwatukw ram…ômis…ô p…®k tukwe.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 1Kor 10:13, Jut 6\x*Narimnari me n…ôha ramahat…ôn m…ô I…ôr…®m…ônu rukur…ôn nuvehim…®ruien n…ôrmama me s…ôm…ôme kamh…ôsiai in, mamho noien me s…ô in rokeikei, n…ôn…ô rukur…ôn n…®peki rakaien ir…ôha ia n…ôr…ôhaien s…ô kamhar…ô ir…ô. M…ôt…ô n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme h…ôpkatukwatukw mh…ô Kumwes…ôn rukur…ôn n…ôrpw…®nien noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônraha t…ôkwt…ôkwuni, mar…ô mo tukuaha…° mwi ir…ôha r…ômwhen ia n…ôrmama ia kalapus, mamev…ôn meste in truvei pen n…ôrpw…®nien sampam m…®nraha ia n…ôp…®n kurir…ô.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 2:10 \xt Jut 7-8,16\x*Kumwes…ôn truvei pen n…ôrpw…®nien m n…ôrmama …ôr…ôha me pam, m…ôt…ô truvei pen n…ôrpw…®nien asori m…®nraha n…ôha s…ôm…ôme kamhesi pen noien …ômkem…®k me n…®pwranraha rokeikei p…®k, mamh…ôt…ô …ôr…ôha nasoriien s…ô kauvehi kam…ôr…®m…ônu ir…ô.  
\p Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha s…ôm…ôme iakam…ô…°kiari ia nir…ôha, ir…ôha kamh…ôrpwi ir…ôha, mamho k…ônkapw…ônraha, mamh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien …ôr…ôha me ia na…°elo me ia neiai mh…ôpw…ôh nehek…®rien.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Jut 9\x*N…ôri au…ôr a m…ô na…°elo me n…ôha ir…ôha h…ôskai n…ôn…ô n…ô…°senraha rasori m…ôpi raka n…ôrmama me n…ôha, m…ôt…ô ir…ôha h…ôpk…®ni …ôr…ôha mh…ô ir…ôha riti ia n…ômri I…ôr…®m…ônu.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Jut 10\x*M…ôt…ô nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha kamh…ôni …ôr…ôha narimnari me s…ôm…ôme ir…ôha h…ôpkukur…ôn mh…ô. Ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia n…ôri …ôprm…®n me n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha riw…ôn, m…ôt…ô kamho a nari s…ô hokeikei. N…ôri …ôprm…®n me n…ôha k…®m…ôkw…ôhi ir…ôha m…ô kw…ônkru trousi t…ôrini ir…ôha, kousi …ôpune ir…ôha. Kumwes…ôn trouraha mwi nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha r…ômwhen ia n…ôri …ôprm…®n me n…ôha.   
\p
\v 13 \x - \xo 2:13 \xt Jut 12\x*In tr…ôr…ôku ir…ôha ia n…ôr…ôhaien t…® n…ôri n…ô m…ô ir…ôha h…ôno n…ôr…ôhaien m n…ôrmama. Ia n…ôt…ôien s…ôv…ônraha noien i ramasan p…®k m…ô ia rukw…ôsik…ôr tuhani p…®k nari mh…ôn…®mwi p…®k. Ir…ôha h…ômwhen ia t…®nari …ômkem…®k, u…ô t…ômwki n…®mwapw s…ô ramo aur…®s k…®miaha. Ir…ôha h…ôuvehe mhani nari k…®miaha m…®nraha, m…ôt…ô kamheiku…ô ia k…®miaha rer…®nraha ra…°ien a.  
\v 14 Ia n…ômr…®nraha kamh…ôt…ô p…®k n…®pran me, mamhakres ir…ôha, mh…ôpkapw…®s mh…ô ia noien …ôr…ôha. Ir…ôha kamh…ôvi n…ôrmama s…ôm…ôme n…ôt…ôr…®…°ien s…ôv…ônraha r…®pk…®skai mh…ô m…ô tuh…ôuv…ôn mho noien …ôr…ôha. Rer…®nraha rokeikei p…®k mane. K…®nahat…ôn amasan ir…ôha ir…ô. Ir…ôha n…®pwn…ôti n…ôr…ôhaien Kumwes…ôn ram…ôkwein …ôr…ôha ia nir…ôha!  
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt Nam 22:7, Jut 11, Rev 2:14\x*Ir…ôha h…ôn…ôpw…ôh suatuk s…ô ratukwatukw, n…ôn…ô mh…ôikou mamhesi pen suatuk s…ôv…ôi Palam t…®ni Peor, i…ôrmama s…ô rokeikei p…®k nuvehiien mane ia noien …ôr…ôha.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Nam 22:28-35\x*M…ôt…ô to…°ki riti r…®n…ôski t…® noien …ôr…ôha me s…ôv…ônhi. K…®taha s…ôukur…ôn m…ô to…°ki r…®pk…ô…°kiari mh…ô, m…ôt…ô Kumwes…ôn r…®no to…°ki r…ô…°kiari ia reri i…ôrmama m…ô tr…®nise noien ikou s…ôv…ôi profet n…ôha.   
\p
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt Jut 12-13\x*Nahat…ôn eiku…ô me n…ôha h…ômwhen ia n…ômri nui me s…ôm…ôme h…ônam…ô, u…ô n…ôpu…ô s…ô n…®m…ôta…°i r…®m…ôpeki raka n…ôn…ô nes…ôn riw…ôn ir…ô. Kumwes…ôn r…®n…ôpn…ôpen…ô raka ia n…ôpit…ôvien asori m…ô s…ôv…ônraha.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 2:18 \xt Jut 16\x*Ir…ôha kamh…ôfi…ôut…ô ia nir…ôha me, mamh…ôni n…ô…°kiariien arm…ôri me, mamh…ôvi n…ôm…ô me s…ôm…ôme h…ôpkaraka a i ia n…ôkur kamhar…ô ia n…ôpit…ôvien m…ô tuh…ôuvehe mho noien …ôr…ôha me s…ô ramo naur…®sien n…®pwranraha rokeikei p…®k.  
